data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Grasmere, Staten Island! Step inside this fully detached single-family home and be greeted by a warm and inviting foyer, leading you seamlessly into a spacious living room, dining area, and kitchen. This charming residence features 3 bedrooms, offering versatility and comfort for your lifestyle needs. The fully finished basement, complete with a convenient separate entrance, features a 3/4 bathroom, providing an ideal space for guests! Transform the third bedroom into your own sanctuary or maintain its current functionality as a productive workspace. Indulge in luxury with your very own jacuzzi in the full bathroom, promising relaxation and rejuvenation after a long day. Outside, a private driveway awaits, accommodating up to two cars with ease, ensuring hassle-free parking for you and your guests. Convenience is key with this prime location, offering proximity to an array of amenities including shops, restaurants, parks, and more. Schedule your viewing today and make this Grasmere gem your forever home!
